---
const preorderBooks = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Jeans",
    author: "Kerri Maniscalco",
    cover: "/src/assets/img/jean.png",
    releaseDate: "15 de junio, 2023",
    price: "200 bs",
    discount: "150 bs"
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Chamarra Cuero",
    author: "Victoria Álvarez",
    cover: "/src/assets/img/chamarra1.jpg",
    releaseDate: "30 de junio, 2023",
    price: "300 bs",
    discount: "210 bs"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "Falda",
    author: "Mónica Gutiérrez",
    cover: "/src/assets/img/falda1.png",
    releaseDate: "10 de julio, 2023",
    price: "350 bs",
    discount: "260 bs"
  }
];
---

<section>
  <div class="pt-16 pb-16 bg-gray-100 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero section with title -->
    <div class="bg-gray-200 py-12 mb-8 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-1/4">
        <img
          src="/books-stack.png"
          alt="Pila de libros"
          class="h-full object-cover object-left"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">PREVENTAS</h1>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Reserva ahora los próximos cambios de temporada. Envío prioritario el día de publicación.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Left sidebar with promotional text -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">¡Reserva con anticipación!</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Asegura tu ropa favorita más antes de su lanzamiento. Preventas con descuentos exclusivos y envío prioritario.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Sé el primero en disfrutar los nuevos modelos  más esperadas del año.
            </p>
            <a href="/todas-preventas" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-6 rounded-md transition-colors">
              Todas las Preventas
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-yellow-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              ¿Cómo funcionan las preventas?
            </h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Reserva ahora y paga al precio de preventa (con descuento)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Recibirás tu libro el mismo día de su lanzamiento</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Envío prioritario para clientes de preventa</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Cancela tu reserva sin coste hasta 7 días antes del lanzamiento</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right content with book cards -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            {preorderBooks.map((book) => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md relative group">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-1 px-3 rounded-bl-lg z-10 transform rotate-0 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-3">
                  PREVENTA
                </div>

                <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
                  <img
                    src={book.cover || "/placeholder.svg?height=400&width=300"}
                    alt={book.title}
                    class="w-full h-64 object-cover transform transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
                  />
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-end justify-center">
                    <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 mb-4 rounded-md transition-colors">
                      Reservar ahora
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-4">
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">{book.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2">{book.author}</p>

                  <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Lanzamiento: {book.releaseDate}</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-3">
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-gray-500 line-through text-sm">{book.price}</span>
                      <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold ml-2">{book.discount}</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded">
                      Ahorra 15%
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Featured preorder -->
          <div class="mt-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-center">
              <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <span class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
                  PREVENTA DESTACADA
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">La Última Profecía</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                  La esperada conclusión de la trilogía "Los Guardianes del Tiempo" de la aclamada autora Elena Fuentes. Una aventura épica que ha cautivado a millones de lectores en todo el mundo.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Lanzamiento: 5 de agosto, 2023</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <span class="text-gray-500 line-through text-sm">24,90€</span>
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl ml-2">19,90€</span>
                  </div>
                  <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-6 rounded-md transition-colors">
                    Reservar con 20% descuento
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-center">
                <img
                  src="/books/ultima-profecia.jpg"
                  alt="La Última Profecía"
                  class="h-64 object-cover rounded-md shadow-lg transform -rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- More books button -->
          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/todas-preventas" class="inline-block bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-900 text-white font-medium py-3 px-8 rounded-md transition-colors">
              Ver todas las preventas
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
